                      "name": "ovT",
                      "fill": "$--foreground",
                      "textGrowth": "fixed-width",
                      "width": "fill_container",
                      "content": "如果把上海中学放在全市高中版图里，它属于‘目标明确型家庭’最先重点研究的一类学校。",
                      "lineHeight": 1.14,
                      "fontFamily": "Newsreader",
                      "fontSize": 34,
                      "fontWeight": "600"
                    },
                    {
                      "type": "text",
                      "id": "KqzJu",
                      "name": "ovD",
                      "fill": "$--muted-foreground",
                      "textGrowth": "fixed-width",
                      "width": "fill_container",
                      "content": "它的吸引力并不只在于名气，而在于完整的课程深度、学术资源与学生群体环境。与此同时，家长也会担心学习压力、竞争氛围与是否真正匹配孩子个性。",
                      "lineHeight": 1.7,
                      "fontFamily": "Geist",
                      "fontSize": 16,
                      "fontWeight": "normal"
                    }
                  ]
                },
                {
                  "type": "frame",
                  "id": "WvbwO",
                  "name": "admission",
                  "width": "fill_container",
                  "fill": "$--card",
                  "stroke": {
                    "align": "inside",
                    "thickness": 1,
                    "fill": "$--border"
                  },
                  "layout": "vertical",
                  "gap": 14,
                  "padding": 24,
                  "children": [
                    {
                      "type": "text",
                      "id": "TLOyO",
                      "name": "adK",
                      "fill": "$--primary",
                      "content": "招生与升学路径",
                      "fontFamily": "JetBrains Mono",
                      "fontSize": 12,
                      "fontWeight": "500"
                    },
                    {
                      "type": "text",
                      "id": "yQd0V",
                      "name": "adT",
                      "fill": "$--foreground",
                      "textGrowth": "fixed-width",
                      "width": "fill_container",
                      "content": "家长最关心的，通常不是学校‘好不好’，而是孩子有没有现实进入路径。",
                      "lineHeight": 1.15,
                      "fontFamily": "Newsreader",
                      "fontSize": 32,
                      "fontWeight": "600"
                    },
                    {
                      "type": "text",
                      "id": "1eta4",
                      "name": "ad1",
                      "fill": "$--muted-foreground",
                      "textGrowth": "fixed-width",
                      "width": "fill_container",
                      "content": "1. 先看招生批次与政策口径。学校名气越高，越需要先判断是否存在现实可行路径，而不是只被榜单吸引。",
                      "lineHeight": 1.7,
                      "fontFamily": "Geist",
                      "fontSize": 15,
                      "fontWeight": "normal"
                    },
                    {
                      "type": "text",
                      "id": "7x3FZ",
                      "name": "ad2",
                      "fill": "$--muted-foreground",
                      "textGrowth": "fixed-width",
                      "width": "fill_container",
                      "content": "2. 再看校内课程与孩子能力结构是否匹配。学术节奏快、要求高的学校，并不适合所有类型的优秀学生。",
                      "lineHeight": 1.7,
                      "fontFamily": "Geist",
                      "fontSize": 15,
                      "fontWeight": "normal"
                    },
                    {
                      "type": "text",
                      "id": "qLHKR",
                      "name": "ad3",
                      "fill": "$--muted-foreground",
                      "textGrowth": "fixed-width",
                      "width": "fill_container",
                      "content": "3. 最后看通勤、住宿、校园文化与长期发展感受。这些通常决定学生三年体验是否稳定。",
                      "lineHeight": 1.7,
                      "fontFamily": "Geist",
                      "fontSize": 15,
                      "fontWeight": "normal"
                    }
                  ]
                },
                {
                  "type": "frame",
                  "id": "y1BNF",
                  "name": "curr",
                  "width": "fill_container",
                  "fill": "$--foreground",
                  "layout": "vertical",
