                      "content": "课程结构",
                      "fontFamily": "JetBrains Mono",
                      "fontSize": 12,
                      "fontWeight": "500"
                    },
                    {
                      "type": "text",
                      "id": "96g3d",
                      "name": "cuT",
                      "fill": "$--background",
                      "textGrowth": "fixed-width",
                      "width": "fill_container",
                      "content": "偏研究型、偏学术型的学生，往往能在这里吃到更多课程资源红利。",
                      "lineHeight": 1.14,
                      "fontFamily": "Newsreader",
                      "fontSize": 30,
                      "fontWeight": "600"
                    },
                    {
                      "type": "text",
                      "id": "9eIJ9",
                      "name": "cuD",
                      "fill": "$--background",
                      "textGrowth": "fixed-width",
                      "width": "fill_container",
                      "content": "常见关注点包括：竞赛与拔尖培养资源是否集中、基础学科深度是否足够、研究型项目比例、国际理解课程与综合素养活动是否均衡。",
                      "lineHeight": 1.65,
                      "fontFamily": "Geist",
                      "fontSize": 15,
                      "fontWeight": "normal"
                    }
                  ]
                },
                {
                  "type": "frame",
