                      "fill": "$--foreground",
                      "textGrowth": "fixed-width",
                      "width": "fill_container",
                      "content": "Q1. 这所学校更适合‘竞赛型’还是‘全面型’学生？",
                      "lineHeight": 1.6,
                      "fontFamily": "Geist",
                      "fontSize": 16,
                      "fontWeight": "500"
                    },
                    {
                      "type": "text",
                      "id": "B0riN",
                      "name": "faqA1",
                      "fill": "$--muted-foreground",
                      "textGrowth": "fixed-width",
                      "width": "fill_container",
                      "content": "更准确的说法是：它更适合能在高要求环境中保持稳定输出的学生。竞赛资源是优势，但不是唯一判断标准。",
                      "lineHeight": 1.65,
                      "fontFamily": "Geist",
                      "fontSize": 15,
                      "fontWeight": "normal"
                    },
                    {
                      "type": "text",
                      "id": "Ti3C6",
                      "name": "faqQ2",
                      "fill": "$--foreground",
                      "textGrowth": "fixed-width",
                      "width": "fill_container",
                      "content": "Q2. 家长最容易忽视什么？",
                      "lineHeight": 1.6,
                      "fontFamily": "Geist",
                      "fontSize": 16,
                      "fontWeight": "500"
                    },
                    {
                      "type": "text",
                      "id": "h9qCf",
                      "name": "faqA2",
                      "fill": "$--muted-foreground",
                      "textGrowth": "fixed-width",
                      "width": "fill_container",
                      "content": "很多家长会高估学校名气带来的确定性，却低估孩子是否真的适应这种节奏与氛围。",
                      "lineHeight": 1.65,
                      "fontFamily": "Geist",
                      "fontSize": 15,
                      "fontWeight": "normal"
                    },
                    {
                      "type": "text",
