                      "content": "建议阅读顺序是：先看规则类概念，再看路径类概念，最后看策略类概念。只有这样，后面的新闻和问答才不会越看越乱。",
                      "lineHeight": 1.7,
                      "fontFamily": "Geist",
                      "fontSize": 18,
                      "fontWeight": "normal"
                    }
                  ]
                },
                {
                  "type": "frame",
                  "id": "esA2X",
                  "name": "scenes",
                  "width": "fill_container",
                  "fill": "#111111",
                  "cornerRadius": 16,
                  "layout": "vertical",
                  "gap": 14,
                  "padding": 24,
                  "children": [
                    {
                      "type": "text",
                      "id": "VRThJ",
                      "fill": "$--primary",
                      "content": "如何使用总表",
                      "fontFamily": "JetBrains Mono",
                      "fontSize": 13,
                      "fontWeight": "500"
                    },
                    {
                      "type": "text",
                      "id": "tLGJ5",
                      "fill": "$--background",
                      "textGrowth": "fixed-width",
                      "width": "fill_container",
                      "content": "如果你看到一条新闻却不知道它在说什么，就回到这页先找到对应概念；如果你已经知道概念名，就顺着关联概念继续补足判断框架。",
                      "lineHeight": 1.7,
                      "fontFamily": "Geist",
                      "fontSize": 18,
                      "fontWeight": "normal"
                    }
                  ]
                },
                {
                  "type": "frame",
                  "id": "jXCt9",
                  "name": "misread",
                  "width": "fill_container",
                  "fill": "$--card",
                  "stroke": {
                    "align": "inside",
                    "thickness": 1,
                    "fill": "$--border"
                  },
                  "layout": "vertical",
                  "gap": 14,
                  "padding": 24,
                  "children": [
                    {
                      "type": "text",
                      "id": "SMu4i",
                      "fill": "$--primary",
                      "content": "概念分组",
                      "fontFamily": "JetBrains Mono",
                      "fontSize": 13,
                      "fontWeight": "500"
                    },
                    {
                      "type": "text",
                      "id": "Hzvwg",
                      "fill": "$--muted-foreground",
                      "textGrowth": "fixed-width",
                      "width": "fill_container",
                      "content": "规则类：报名资格、名额分配到校、平行志愿。\n路径类：自招、综合评价、统一录取。\n策略类：梯度、承接、校内竞争、区内差异。",
                      "lineHeight": 1.7,
                      "fontFamily": "Geist",
                      "fontSize": 18,
                      "fontWeight": "normal"
                    }
                  ]
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "type": "frame",
              "id": "Ag3Aa",
              "name": "side",
              "width": 360,
              "layout": "vertical",
              "gap": 20,
              "children": [
                {
                  "type": "frame",
                  "id": "RNMA7",
                  "name": "judge box",
                  "width": "fill_container",
                  "fill": "#111111",
                  "cornerRadius": 16,
                  "layout": "vertical",
                  "gap": 14,
                  "padding": 24,
                  "children": [
                    {
                      "type": "text",
                      "id": "OqV3S",
                      "fill": "$--primary",
                      "content": "先看哪几个概念",
                      "fontFamily": "JetBrains Mono",
                      "fontSize": 13,
                      "fontWeight": "500"
                    },
                    {
                      "type": "text",
                      "id": "x49Ro",
                      "fill": "$--background",
                      "textGrowth": "fixed-width",
                      "width": "fill_container",
                      "content": "1. 报名资格\n2. 名额分配到校\n3. 平行志愿\n4. 自招 / 综合评价",
                      "lineHeight": 1.7,
                      "fontFamily": "Geist",
                      "fontSize": 17,
                      "fontWeight": "normal"
                    }
                  ]
                },
                {
                  "type": "frame",
                  "id": "BrrUN",
                  "name": "related concepts",
                  "width": "fill_container",
                  "fill": "$--card",
                  "stroke": {
                    "align": "inside",
                    "thickness": 1,
                    "fill": "$--border"
                  },
                  "layout": "vertical",
                  "gap": 12,
                  "padding": 22,
                  "children": [
                    {
                      "type": "text",
                      "id": "YhLUf",
                      "fill": "$--primary",
                      "content": "关联概念索引",
                      "fontFamily": "JetBrains Mono",
                      "fontSize": 13,
                      "fontWeight": "500"
                    },
                    {
                      "type": "text",
                      "id": "3blxh",
                      "fill": "$--muted-foreground",
                      "textGrowth": "fixed-width",
                      "width": "fill_container",
                      "content": "报名资格：先决定你能不能进入这套规则。\n名额分配到校：理解校内竞争和招生计划。\n平行志愿：理解排序与承接。\n自招 / 综合评价：理解学校主动筛选路径。",
                      "lineHeight": 1.7,
                      "fontFamily": "Geist",
                      "fontSize": 16,
                      "fontWeight": "normal"
                    }
                  ]
                },
                {
                  "type": "frame",
                  "id": "uDIRu",
                  "name": "一页记忆",
                  "width": "fill_container",
                  "fill": "#FFFFFF",
                  "stroke": {
                    "align": "inside",
                    "thickness": 1,
                    "fill": "#CBCCC9"
                  },
                  "layout": "vertical",
                  "gap": 10,
                  "padding": 20,
                  "children": [
                    {
                      "type": "text",
                      "id": "K3oyK",
                      "fill": "#111111",
                      "content": "阅读顺序",
                      "fontFamily": "Newsreader",
                      "fontSize": 24,
                      "fontWeight": "600"
                    },
                    {
                      "type": "text",
                      "id": "sHOIP",
                      "fill": "#111111",
                      "textGrowth": "fixed-width",
                      "width": "fill_container",
                      "content": "先看规则类，再看路径类，不要一上来先研究学校偏好。",
                      "fontFamily": "Geist",
                      "fontSize": 14,
                      "fontWeight": "500"
                    },
                    {
                      "type": "text",
                      "id": "Vo90N",
                      "fill": "#111111",
                      "textGrowth": "fixed-width",
                      "width": "fill_container",
                      "content": "看新闻时遇到术语不懂，先回到总表确认定义和适用场景。",
                      "fontFamily": "Geist",
                      "fontSize": 14,
                      "fontWeight": "500"
                    },
                    {
                      "type": "text",
                      "id": "mo4wq",
                      "fill": "#111111",
                      "textGrowth": "fixed-width",
                      "width": "fill_container",
                      "content": "做具体决策前，再跳去问答页、时间轴页和学校页。",
                      "fontFamily": "Geist",
                      "fontSize": 14,
                      "fontWeight": "500"
                    }
                  ]
                }
              ]
            }
